headline: Morgan Stanley Sees Near-Term Rally Ahead — Here Are 2 Stocks to Bet on It
summary: Markets have proven highly volatile in the first two months of President Trump’s new term of office, as investors are worried about everything from trade and tariff policy to increased inflation to geopolitics. But there are some green lights flashing on the market dashboard. For starters, the prices of some staple goods are coming down – prices are dropping for both gasoline and eggs, for instance – and in the past two weeks, markets have turned back upward.
